flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Initiate[Ordering Department triggers order generation]
  Initiate --> FetchPlan[Retrieve active Allocation Plan]
  FetchPlan --> Group[Group allocation lines by Import Site]
  Group --> Compose[Compose Overseas Order for each Site]
  Compose --> SetMeans[Specify delivery means ship/air]
  SetMeans --> Transmit[Transmit official orders to selected Sites]
  Transmit --> Process[Sites receive and process orders]
  Process --> Ack[Sites send Acknowledgements back]
  Ack --> Update[System updates Order status to Transmitted]
  Update --> End([End])
